him to death, right?

53:09.969 --> 53:12.058
-He deserves it.
-You got somewhere to be,

53:12.101 --> 53:13.886
like, school, and maybe
clean your mess up?

53:13.929 --> 53:15.322
Mama, I know
what the death penalty is--

53:15.366 --> 53:16.976
I can't believe you're actually
thinking about

53:17.019 --> 53:18.020
visiting a murderer.

53:18.064 --> 53:19.152
-I didn't say--
-That is so gross.

53:19.196 --> 53:20.153
I didn't say he was innocent.

53:21.589 --> 53:22.634
-Okay, then what are you saying?
-He's a human being.

53:23.852 --> 53:25.463
Okay, I'm late.
Dave's gonna drop me.

53:25.506 --> 53:27.029
So, are you seeing your dad,
later?

53:27.378 --> 53:28.553
No, the Gremlins will be there.

53:28.596 --> 53:30.772
Well, they are your
brother and sister.

53:32.296 --> 53:33.253
What?

53:33.775 --> 53:34.994
Fine. I'll go.

53:35.429 --> 53:36.822
All right.
Am I getting you later?

53:36.865 --> 53:38.258
No,
Dave's gonna drive me.

53:38.302 --> 53:39.868
Well, will you call me,
please, miss?

53:39.912 --> 53:41.174
Mom, I got soccer practice
till 6:00

53:41.218 --> 53:42.784
-and I'm taking the bus.
-Okay, well I thought

53:42.828 --> 53:44.003
-I was getting you.
- Bye.

53:44.046 --> 53:45.222
What about oatmeal?

