55:19.141 --> 55:21.013
Oh, nice to meet you too,
Cameron.

55:21.405 --> 55:22.754
Folks call me Todd.

55:23.494 --> 55:25.365
Oh, yeah? Todd.

55:25.713 --> 55:28.063
I really appreciate you
coming all this way.

55:29.935 --> 55:31.893
-You're in Houston, right?
