about...

56:39.483 --> 56:42.311
your life here,
what it's like or...

56:42.355 --> 56:45.358
-Not much to tell, really.
-Mm, right.

56:47.142 --> 56:49.797
Any comforts or, I don't know?

56:50.537 --> 56:51.582
In jail?

56:52.670 --> 56:53.758
No, ma'am.

56:56.848 --> 57:00.417
